+        # Use fused GEMM on HIP (4x faster than dequantize + matmul on RDNA4)
+        # Block sizes tuned via scripts/sweep_awq_blocks.py on 2x R9700.
+        # Batch-size-dependent dispatch: higher split_k for decode (small M),
